---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import logoImage from '../../assets/logo.png';
---

<Layout title="About Susan Hale">
  <main class="bg-white">
    <section class="pt-40 pb-24 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-boho-navy mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">Susan Hale</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-boho-gold font-barlow tracking-widest uppercase mb-12 border-b border-boho-wheat pb-6">
          Escalation Intelligence & Clinical Resilience
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-boho-navy/80 font-sans leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Susan Hale is a SFC Paratrooper, a Combat Veteran with three deployments, and a Doctor of Medical Science candidate specializing in Human Resilience. Her background spans nearly 14 years of honorable military service, where she excelled in Military Intelligence, physical security for international dignitaries, and casualty assistance.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            While the military environment is often defined by intensity and conflict, Susan balances this operational background with her work as a Licensed Acupuncturist, Certified Acupuncture Detoxification Specialist, and Chinese Herbalist. Her focus remains on helping individuals restore their structural and emotional stability.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-boho-denim/10 p-8 my-10 border-l-4 border-boho-denim">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-boho-navy mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">Navigating High-Conflict Spaces</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-boho-navy/80">
              Susan has faced systemic challenges and judgment within high-conflict environments—from managing emergency responses as a Senior Desk Sergeant to navigating complex interpersonal dynamics in the military. Rather than becoming hardened by these environments, she learned how to stay clear, functional, and grounded. She bridges high-stress operations with a commitment to maintaining high ethical standards and genuine human care.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p>
            At Star and Stream, Susan uses her clinical and operational experience to teach Escalation Intelligence and Resilience. She helps people learn how to survive intense environments, achieve their goals, and maintain a thoughtful, steady focus in their professional and personal lives.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
